{"uuid":"e46defc5-705d-4ecc-83d2-f238e6232b8a","ownerUuid":"6MGYOlk90tVwng9YxCh71HdlT9E3","description":"I will put test cases for now here:

test cases:

* Accordion

  - [ ] accordion option could be opened text visible
  - [ ] option could be closed (text hidden)
  - [ ] all options rendered
  - [ ] all options could be opened
  - [ ] all options could be opened in multiple modes
  - [ ] only one option could be opened in multiple mode


* Checkbox

  - [ ] onChange called and className changed onClick if DefaultChecked=false
  - [ ] onChange called and className changed onClick if DefaultChecked=true

* Header
  - [ ] alt text visible if source broken
  - [ ] image visible if source exists
* Input
  - [ ] placeholder visible
  - [ ] works with input mode text (some symbols are allowed and some not allowed)
  - [ ] works with input mode email (some symbols are allowed and some not allowed)
  - [ ] works with input mode number (some symbols allowed and some not allowed)
  - [ ] could not be used when disabled
  - [ ] check 'required' logic (does it work correctly)
  - [ ] check how to work when props.value and props.onChange exists at the same time
* Link
  - [ ] value rendered correctly
  - [ ] link leads to the right place
* Modal 
  - [ ] modal could be opened and closed by clicking on the grey background
  - [ ] modal could be closed by clicking on the cross
  - [ ] content rendered
* Notification
  - [ ] content rendered
  - [ ] specify what is foreground and check it works correctly
  - [ ] specify what is background and check it works correctly
* Select
  - [ ] onChange triggered if some option selected
  - [ ] selected value visible
* Sidebar
  - [ ] could be opened and closed by clicking on the grey background
  - [ ] could be closed by clicking on the cross
  - [ ] content rendered
*. Table
  - [ ] table headers rendered in the right way
  - [ ] data rendered in the right way
*. Title
  - [ ] text rendered
  - [ ] appropriate level exists on the page (check semantics)
* Tooltip
  - [ ] content rendered
  - [ ] too long content (text) hidden ","isDone":false}

{"uuid":"33e37b7f-cdc9-4bc9-b91b-2f64f4e350a7","description":"Expected version: 8.9.2
Got: 8.14.1

This is happening because the package's manifest has an engines.pnpm field specified.
To fix this issue, install the required pnpm version globally.
